generate.userPrompt:
Based on the following summary, write the complete text for the narrative section:

Summary: {summary}

Book Context:
Title: {bookTitle}
Chapter: {chapterTitle}
Section: {sectionTitle}

Tags/Themes: {tags}

Write a detailed and engaging narrative text that develops this summary. Use literary language appropriate to the genre.

summarize.userPrompt:
Create a concise summary of the following text, capturing the main points:

{text}

Create a summary in a single paragraph, highlighting the most important events and ideas.

expand.userPrompt:
Expand the following text, adding more details, descriptions, and development:

{text}

Maintain the original style and tone, but make the narrative richer and more detailed. Add sensory descriptions, character emotions, and environmental details.

rewrite.userPrompt:
Rewrite the following text improving clarity, flow, and narrative impact:

{text}

Keep the same information and tone, but improve the writing quality. Fix style issues, repetitions, and make the text more elegant.

changePOV.userPrompt:
Rewrite the following text changing the point of view to: {targetPOV}

Original text:
{text}

Keep the content and events, but adapt the narrative perspective. If first person, use the main character's voice. If third person, maintain appropriate distance.

continueStory.userPrompt:
Continue the following story in a natural and engaging way:

{text}

Write the next paragraph or section, maintaining the style, tone, and narrative rhythm. Continue events in a logical and interesting manner.

addDialogue.userPrompt:
Add natural dialogue to the following narrative text:

{text}

Insert dialogues between characters that are relevant and natural to the context. Use quotation marks for speech. Dialogues should reveal personality, advance the plot, or create tension.

improveDescription.userPrompt:
Improve the descriptions in the following text, adding more sensory details:

{text}

Add more vivid descriptions of settings, characters, and environments. Use all five senses (sight, hearing, smell, touch, taste) to create immersion. Be specific and avoid clich√©s.

createScene.userPrompt:
Create a complete scene based on the following information:

Context: {context}
Characters: {characters}
Scene objective: {objective}

Write an engaging scene with environment description, character actions, and dialogue when appropriate. The scene should have a beginning, middle, and end.

developCharacter.userPrompt:
Develop the following character more deeply within the scene context:

Text/Scene: {text}
Character: {character}

Add internal thoughts, emotions, motivations, and character reactions. Show their personality through actions, dialogue, and internal reflections.

addTension.userPrompt:
Rewrite the following text adding more tension and suspense:

{text}

Increase conflict, create uncertainty, add obstacles, or reveal information gradually. Use narrative techniques to keep the reader engaged and anxious about what comes next.

fixPacing.userPrompt:
Adjust the pacing of the following text as indicated:

{text}

Desired pacing: {pacingType}
(fast: short sentences, direct action / slow: detailed descriptions, reflections / balanced: mix of both)

Rewrite the text adjusting sentence length, amount of description, and narrative focus to achieve the desired pacing.
